• 2-5 years of experience in software engineering roles using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

• Experience using git with Github for version control and source code management.

• Experience turning user stories and product requirements into design concepts and development tasks.

• Able to take a software project from idea through requirements gathering, design, planning, development, testing, to deployment independently.

• Familiarity with development practices like unit testing, linting, code reviews, and pair programming.

• Familiarity with REST APIs (building, consuming, or both) and working with JSON objects as data stores.

• Experience with modern web technologies, like React, Vue, or Angular (React preferred).

• Basic experience in using cutting edge React patterns such as Hooks, Context, and await/async.

• Familiarity with design systems (Material UI, Ant, Bootstrap).
